{"serial": "12022", "department_serial": 11, "code": "EL4069", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Topics in Linguistics I", "ch": "語言學專題I"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Li, Ming-Yi"], "ch": ["李明懿"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 3, "session": ["6", "7", "8"]}, "loc": {"building": "A", "room": "112"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 50, "department": {"ch": "英美語文學系", "en": "Department of English"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 0, "selected": 28, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "#本課程之實際教學目標和內容將於開學後三周內定案。\n\n本課程主要目的在於介紹語言對比分析的方法和應用。修習完畢並通過學期成績評量的學生應能：\n1. 認識對比分析的理論基礎；\n2. 透過對比分析探索中、英語的語法特性；\n3. 將對比分析應用於第二語言教學。", "en": "# The actual teaching objectives and content of this course will be finalized within three weeks after the start of the semester.\nThe main purpose of this course is to introduce the methods and applications of comparative language analysis. Students who have completed the course and passed the semester grade assessment should be able to:\n1. Understand the theoretical basis of contrastive analysis (CA);\n2. Explore the typological characteristics of Chinese and English through CA;\n3. Applying CA to second language teaching."}, "outline": {"ch": "單元       講題\n1對比分析的理論基礎\n2偏誤分析的理論基礎和中介語\n3語言遷移和跨語言影響\n4對比分析的方法和內容\n5中、英語言類型的特性\n6              對比分析、偏誤分析與教學應用", "en": "1 Theoretical basis of Contrastive analysis\n2 Theoretical basis of error analysis and interlanguage\n3 Language transfer and cross-language influence\n4 Methods and contents of Contrastive analysis\n5 Contrastive analysis of Mandarin Chinese and English\n6 Contrastive analysis, error analysis and teaching application"}, "textbook": {"ch": "主要上課用書：\n陳俊光 (2012) 《對比分析與教學應用》。台北：文鶴。\n潘文國 (2010)《漢英語言對比概論》。商務印書館。\nJames, C. (1980) Contrastive Analysis. Longman.", "en": "The main class book:\n陳俊光 (2012) 《對比分析與教學應用》。台北：文鶴。\n潘文國 (2010)《漢英語言對比概論》。商務印書館。\nJames, C. (1980) Contrastive Analysis. Longman."}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "20%", "en": "20%"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n研討\n\n個別指導", "en": ["Lecture", "Seminar", "", "Individual Instruction"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "課程參與60％\n    出席狀況 (10％)\n    課堂表現(20％)\n    作業與課後討論 (30％)\n專題40％", "en": "Class participation 60％\nattending (10％)\n        class performance (20％)\nassignment and report (30％)\nProject 40％"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "週二11:00-12:00、週三四13:00-14:00", "en": "11:00-12:00 on Tuesday and 13:00—14:00 on Wednesday and Thursday"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "16+2", "en": "16+2"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "本課程之課堂活動為16週，個別研究輔導為2週。", "en": "The class activities for this course last for 16 weeks, and for another two weeks, the teacher will provide individual tutoring on the research report."}, "domain": {"ch": "語言學與英語教學", "en": "語言學與英語教學"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "英文閱讀解析與寫作論述", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現", "自我評量/同儕互評", "作品/創作展演"]}, {"competencies": "英語溝通與文化跨越", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "審美欣賞與多元創意", "rating": "(1)非常低", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "人文思維與社會關懷", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "組織能力與人際合作", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["出席/課堂表現", "自我評量/同儕互評"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "English critical reading and analytical writing", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Assignments", "Presentation/Oral Exam", "Research Report(printed on paper)", "Attendance/Performance", "Self Assessment/ Peer Assessment", "Products/Creative Performance"]}, {"competencies": "English oral communication and cultural crossing", "rating": "(3)Medium", "assesments": ["Assignments", "Presentation/Oral Exam", "Research Report(printed on paper)", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "aesthetic